Summary.
There are no "close", "minimize" or "maximize" buttons available in the app.


Description.
Steps to reproduce: 
1) Launch application "File Manager"; 
2) Close, minimize or maximize the app. 

Expected result:
There are "close", "minimize" or "maximize" buttons in the app. 
Actual result: 
There are no buttons "close", "minimize" or "maximize" available in the app.

Severity: normal